flowchart TD
  H[home-work] --> V[Tap VSA]
  V --> VS[vehicle-search · V576AE]
  VS --> VSA[stall-default]
  VSA --> OF[odometer-manual-filled]
  OF --> CD[cleaning-default]
  CD --> IP[cleaning-in-progress]
  IP --> CC[cleaning-complete]
  CC --> FD[fueling-default]
  FD --> FU[fueling-unlocking]
  FU --> IP2[fueling-in-progress · no pump telemetry]
  IP2 --> FC[fueling-complete · manual]
  FC --> ST[stall assignment]
  ST --> FAC{Facilitator: stall issue}
  FAC --> SM[stall-missing]
  SM --> SR[stall-issue-reported]
  SR --> SC[stall-complete]
  SC --> FIN[Footer Complete]
